item.description:
This code helps me remove duplicate files, ending with -copy in the folder.
本程序会删除文件夹中以“-copy”结尾的重复文章。
import os arr = os.listdir() target = [] for i in arr: if &quot;- Copy.JPG&quot; in i or &quot;- Copy.jpg&quot; in i or &quot;- Copy.heic&quot; in i or &quot;- Copy.BMP&quot; in i or &quot;- Copy.PNG&quot; in i or &quot;- Copy.png&quot; in i: target.append(i) for t in target: os.remove(t)
